\par\plain { }{\f0\fs24\b1 Grammar, Spelling, Capitalization, & Punctuation}
\par\plain {4: There are no errors in grammar, spelling, capitalization, or punctuation.}
\par\plain {3: There are some errors; however, these errors do not distract the reader.}
\par\plain {2: There are errors that distract the reader.}
\par\plain {1: There are serious errors that interfere with the reader's understanding of the essay.}
